<div class="pairs">
    <p><span class ="small-header">Quick create new player</span></p>
    <span title="If you want to add new user to the system, please fulfill data below and confirm. New user will be instantly visible in the system">
        If there is no user on the list simply create him here
    </span>
    <span class="text-muted">Confirmation will be sent to the new user</span>
    <form class="form-inline" novalidate>
        <div class="form-group">
            <input type="text" id="AddUserName" class="form-control" placeholder="Name and surname">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <input type="email" id="AddUserEmail" class="form-control" placeholder="Email">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info btn-small" id="createNewUserLogin">Create</button>
        <div>
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#noemailhelp">What if you don't know user email? <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign"></i></a>
            @*//todo add mechanism to catch all questions mark and bind help modal info to it*@
            <div id="noemailhelp" class="collapse">
                In the field <strong>Email</strong> type user's nickname or login and then he can contact IGLAclub Team to activate his account.
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </form>
</div>